data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsTVBnU&h=7621e2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/8HdgNc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F8HdgNc&h=7deef38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n補充資料 2：<br />\n香港其實有二十大（如果計 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">QF level 5 degree-issuing</span></span>）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fedu-system%2Fpostsecondary%2Flocal-higher-edu%2Finstitutions%2Findex.html&d=9O0Mso3MwgxO%2BddlTyNxEAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=14387516\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n不過<strong><ins>資助</ins></strong>得 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">UGC 八大</span></span> + <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公帑資助 HKAPA</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港科技大學 HKUST<br />\n香港大學 HKU<br />\n香港中文大學 CUHK<br />\n香港理工大學 PolyU<br />\n香港教育大學 EdUHK<br />\n嶺南大學 LU<br />\n香港浸會大學 HKBU<br />\n香港城市大學 CityU<br />\n<br />\n香港演藝學院 HKAPA</span><br />\n<br />\n香港公開大學 OUHK<br />\n<br />\n香港樹仁大學 Hong Kong Shue Yan University<br />\n東華學院 Tung Wah College<br />\n珠海學院 Chu Hai College<br />\n明愛專上學院 Caritas Institute of Higher Education<br />\n香港能仁專上學院 Hong Kong Nang Yan College of Higher Education<br />\n恒生管理學院 Hang Seng Management College<br />\n明德學院 Centennial College<br />\n宏恩基督教學院 Gratia Christian College<br />\n港專學院 Hong Kong College of Technology<br />\n職業訓練局 - 香港高等教育科技學院 THEi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"謹此補充薛家宴洗板，我唔想評論香港能仁專上學院的校政同宣傳手法<br />\n<br />\n政府政策好清楚: 資助院校資助係院校層面<br />\n<br />\n自資院校資助係課程層面，同埋近年開始有類似OU一直都有的不定期撥款<br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學學術流程和自資院校不一<br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學升格要求同自資院校唔同<br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學對畢業生英文有一定要求，嶺南唔合教資會質保局要求，就要新增IELTS有6.5分先可以畢業的要求，OU經歷甘多次五年一度的評審，學評局幾時有過問學生英文水平，特別係DL<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170226/bkn-20170226095130763-0226_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170226%2Fbkn-20170226095130763-0226_00822_001.html&d=9O0Mso3MwgxO%2BddlTyNxEAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=c0e3084c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170226/bkn-20170226095130763-0226_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n教資會資助大學人均成本係20萬，自資院校為3-6萬<br />\n<br />\n不論是否自資，以同一類型課程比，教資會資助大學人均成本必定高於自資院校，所以張Cert含金量已經唔同，亦都解釋左貼解幾年入面自資院校學額可以升幾倍，係因為真係無勿控制，成本考慮不多之餘，學額的增加同新認可專上學院的註冊門檻太低、限制太少，0收生都唔洗退場(中止營辦資格)，係台灣，註冊率不足60%，人數不足3000人的大專院校已經要退場轉型<br />\n<br />\n以城大所謂自資獸醫做例子，成本35萬，一年收12萬，其餘只能用捐款補貼<a href=\"https://jump.mingpao.com/resources/detail/20170814/s00012/1502677303702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjump.mingpao.com%2Fresources%2Fdetail%2F20170814%2Fs00012%2F1502677303702&d=9O0Mso3MwgxO%2BddlTyNxEAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=23cbb84b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjump.mingpao.com%2Fresources%2Fdetail%2F20170814%2Fs00012%2F1502677303702&h=9e928458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jump.mingpao.com/resources/detail/20170814/s00012/1502677303702</a><br />\n<br />\n所以自資院校係政府角度，是更加容易靈活地因應市場需要，補充資助院校的不足，因為佢地的要求、成本無甘高，基本上可以亂開，例如THEI Civil的學額可收係HKU+POLYU+?的總和<br />\n<br />\n甘就可以順便訓練廉價勞工，但則持有較少人力需求的考慮<br />\n<br />\n自資院校可以賺錢，甚至用黎派股息，學生交學費，有幾多用係學生身上，自己知自已事，所以用錢的靈話性係比較高的"},{"pid":"fd2bfc4348c18a467c6187b74ebed0d4e11df804","tid":736728,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"都唔係香港人讀架啦"},{"pid":"3160cb3e35a5a713135daa1c9e647e44f7fe787e","tid":736728,"uid":166815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"343e856517b121ec5a51c650bc19a03e52e99016","tid":736728,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"否則對歴屆考生極唔公平<br />\n今屆19分都穩入八大<br />\n2012,2013果屆21分都可以冇ugc offer<br />\n<br />\nAgree: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDisagree: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;逆市&rdquo;加位的自資院校應考慮退場轉型，把收生不足的責任推向資助院校並不公平<br />\n<br />\n當年：<br />\n<br />\n珠海學院&ldquo;逆市&rdquo;增四自資學士課程<br />\n<br />\n被問到中學畢業生人數持續下跌，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">校方仍&ldquo;逆市&rdquo;增辦多個課程，校長張忠柟強調，課程是按本港社會需求而開辦，為各界培育人才，相信能吸引學生報讀，不憂慮收生不足問題。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://edu.takungpao.com.hk/q/2015/0320/2950712.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedu.takungpao.com.hk%2Fq%2F2015%2F0320%2F2950712.html&d=9O0Mso3MwgxO%2BddlTyNxEAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=d99209a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://edu.takungpao.com.hk/q/2015/0320/2950712.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今日：<br />\n<br />\n院校學士學位課程近年出現收生不足的問題，2016-17年學年預計第一年學士學位課程收生1040個，最後僅取錄166人，註冊率不足16%。於2017/18學年，院校第一年學士學位課程收生進一步下跌，原預計收生1040人，最終只有123人入讀。<br />\n<br />\n註：台灣大專院校註冊率不足16%，人數不足3000人，需退場轉型<br />\n<br />\n當年：<br />\n<br />\n恒管「逆市」收生人數增　校長：停辦副學士有優勢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/45840/%E6%81%92%E7%AE%A1-%E9%80%86%E5%B8%82-%E6%94%B6%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%A2%9E-%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7-%E5%81%9C%E8%BE%A6%E5%89%AF%E5%AD%B8%E5%A3%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F45840%2F%25E6%2581%2592%25E7%25AE%25A1-%25E9%2580%2586%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A2%259E-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%258B%25A2&d=9O0Mso3MwgxO%2BddlTyNxEAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=e713d02a\" target=\"_blank\